The paper deals with clustering and similarity measures for data sets, which are common topics in several sub-categories of computer science. However, the focus on document similarity and the use of the Rand Index as a measure of cluster similarity suggest that the paper is most likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category. Other relevant sub-categories include Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Databases (cs.DB).
